thing-type.label: UDP connected Nibe F1245 Heat Pump

parameter.name: hostName
parameter.label: Host name
parameter.description: Network address of the Nibe heat pump.

parameter.name: port
parameter.label: UDP port
parameter.description: UDP port to listening data packets from the pump.

parameter.name: refreshInterval
parameter.label: Refresh Interval
parameter.description: States how often a refresh shall occur in seconds.

parameter.name: enableReadCommands
parameter.label: Enable read commands
parameter.description: Enable read commands to read additional variable from Nibe Heat pump which are not included to data readout messages. This is experimental feature, use it at your own risk!

parameter.name: enableWriteCommands
parameter.label: Enable write commands
parameter.description: Enable write commands to change Nibe Heat pump settings. This is experimental feature, use it at your own risk!

parameter.name: serialPort

parameter.name: sendAckToMODBUS40

parameter.label: Enable acknowledges to RMU40 messages
